title: Moso Jamrock
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Caribbean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Authentic Caribbean cooking with vegan choices. The Ital stew as well as the Jamaican Tofu dish are vegetarian due to the cole slaw it comes with, otherwise vegan. The vegan lunch chef serves a daily vegan soup, smoothie and dish of the day. Cozy place with a good vibe.
